    <p>FreshCap uses dual extraction (hot water + alcohol) to capture both water-soluble beta-glucans and alcohol-soluble triterpenes — providing the most complete chemical profile from the fruiting body. Their verified 35%+ beta-glucan content is the highest confirmed concentration among our picks. FreshCap is also one of the most educational mushroom supplement brands, publishing extensive content explaining the fruiting body vs mycelium debate and why beta-glucan verification matters. For informed consumers who understand mushroom supplement science, FreshCap provides the most transparent product.</p>

