    <p>Four Sigmatic combines turkey tail with three other immune-modulating mushrooms — reishi, chaga, and maitake — for broader immunological coverage than a single-species product. Each mushroom activates different immune pathways: turkey tail (PSK/PSP, NK cells), reishi (triterpenes, T-cell modulation), chaga (betulin, antioxidant defense), and maitake (D-fraction, dendritic cell activation). For consumers seeking a comprehensive mushroom immune formula rather than turkey tail alone, Four Sigmatic's multi-species approach is the most strategic.</p>

